Variables:
Global Variables: These are shared by multiple methods of the same class
                  When we want different methods can take same inputs

Parameters      : We don't want to share our variables with other methods of the same class
                  When we want different methods can take different inputs


local variables : We don't want to share our variables with other methods of the same class
                  When you want your methods to give same output for different objects
                  local variables always needs to be initialized while being created,if we are using it.
